---

include _includes/vectors.pug
include _includes/episode.pug

.purple-background
  section.heading
    h1
      span.title Bytes of Good
      include _includes/heart-logo.svg
      span.green Podcast
    :markdown-it
      We cover topics across the social impact spectrum, with incredible guests like Pablo Sarmiento. [Follow us on Spotify](https://open.spotify.com/show/1TNQDtwII6Uv5ojtkOQ7xh) to catch the next episode!
  +section-color-transition('purple-to-white')

section.episodes
  each episode in episodes
    +episode(
      episode.publishedOn,
      episode.listenLink,
      episode.title,
      episode.description,
      episode.guestsCollection.items
    )